      <title>渣打银行中国杠杆融资业务主管 Sam 将离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/standard-chartered-s-china-head-of-leveraged-finance-sam-to-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，渣打银行大中华区及北亚区杠杆、收购融资及私人信贷主管 Vivian Sam 将离职该行。]]></description>
