    <item>
      <title>斯塔默呼吁消除繁文缛节，英国有望批准更多交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/uk-set-to-clear-more-deals-after-starmer-s-call-to-purge-red-tape</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·史塔默 (Keir Starmer) 呼吁监管机构减少繁琐手续以刺激增长后，英国竞争监管机构正在寻找不同的方式，以在不损害消费者利益的情况下批准更多交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/uk-set-to-clear-more-deals-after-starmer-s-call-to-purge-red-tape</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:29:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Citadel 证券将聘请印度区主管和交易员，以推动印度业务发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/citadel-securities-to-hire-operations-head-traders-to-boost-india-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Citadel Securities LLC 计划聘请一名印度业务主管并增加更多交易员，因为这家做市巨头正在扩大其在全球最大股票市场之一的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/citadel-securities-to-hire-operations-head-traders-to-boost-india-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:29:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称 PAG 将以 68 亿美元出售 Airpower 的工业气体部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/pag-said-to-sell-airpower-s-industrial-gas-unit-for-6-8-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，亚洲最大的另类资产管理公司之一 PAG 同意以 68 亿美元的价格将 Airpower Technologies Ltd. 的工业气体业务出售给一个中国财团。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/pag-said-to-sell-airpower-s-industrial-gas-unit-for-6-8-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:25:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
